{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readonly","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-requestProgress"},{"text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":"s about this pack that come from the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"default notification center.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress"},"schemaVersion":{"pa